      {
        "general_idea": "Upgrade Spring Boot parent version to 3.3.2 to align with JDK 21 and Spring Boot 3.x ecosystem.",
        "why_exists": "Spring Boot 3.x requires JDK 17+; using Spring Boot 2.7 with JDK 21 may cause compatibility issues or prevent usage of modern Spring features, and the migration goal explicitly targets Spring Boot 3.3.",
