      {
        "general_idea": "Update Java version property from 11 to 21 to target the new JDK baseline.",
        "why_exists": "Maven compiler plugin uses this property to set source/target compatibility; without this change, the project would compile for JDK 11, failing to utilize JDK 21 features or potentially causing runtime mismatches if the target environment is strictly JDK 21.",
